    • Method Detail

      • onRenderers

        void onRenderers(String[][] trackNames,
                 com.google.android.exoplayer.chunk.MultiTrackChunkSource[] multiTrackSources,
                 com.google.android.exoplayer.TrackRenderer[] renderers)
        Invoked with the results from a ExoMediaPlayer.RendererBuilder.
        Parameters:
        trackNames - The names of the available tracks, indexed by ExoMediaPlayer TYPE_* constants. May be null if the track names are unknown. An individual element may be null if the track names are unknown for the corresponding type.
        multiTrackSources - Sources capable of switching between multiple available tracks, indexed by ExoMediaPlayer TYPE_* constants. May be null if there are no types with multiple tracks. An individual element may be null if it does not have multiple tracks.
        renderers - Renderers indexed by ExoMediaPlayer TYPE_* constants. An individual element may be null if there do not exist tracks of the corresponding type.

      • onRenderersError

        void onRenderersError(Exception e)
        Invoked if a ExoMediaPlayer.RendererBuilder encounters an error.
        Parameters:
        e - Describes the error.
